{
  "title": "Fermented Crispy Russian Apricot Pirozhki",
  "description": "Comforting traditional Russian dish featuring apricot filling, crispy dough, and a hint of fermented flavor. Perfect as a snack or dessert.",
  "cuisine": "Russian",
